{
  "stem": "27031.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We dug in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then my brother, Jack, had to meet my father in a certain farm to get some food.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there, the local Nazis, Ukrainian Nazis, caught my father.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that was the end of Father.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My father hollered to Jack to run.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Jack run away, came back where I was hiding and told me that they caught the father, that was, they killed the father then.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was only two of us left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that was-- could be middle of [PAUSES] '43, then we became orphans, both of us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Then we were hiding in different places, and lots of hardships.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We hardly had a bath and [PAUSES] I guess lots of tears, and we had lots of lice.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The lice were in, uh, my eyebrows, my eyelid, my-- all over the body.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I would go like this, and just like-- surprising didn't get typhus or-- then, but-- but they get used to us after a while.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We couldn't get rid of them because we couldn't go and have a bath.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We were always without the farmer knowing, where we could go and have a little wash up but never-- and also we had nearly the same clothes all the time, never change.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "In the summertime, we would steal fruit from the trees.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "From the gardens, we would steal cucumbers, vegetables.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We would eat-- one day [PAUSES] we were stealing apples.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We were-- and we hear somebody's walking.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And that was-- we look and there's another Jewish guy, Lazarus is his name-- which, he survived also-- and he was hiding in a fire hall, in the ceiling.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And after-- so he said, you could stay with me for-- he was quite a bit older than us.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
